                                  Civil War in South Carolina</strong></a><strong> </strong>-
                                  The State Museum plans a major, four-year retrospective
                                  on the war, beginning with six planned exhibits, two
                  Web sites and a series of programs.              </p>
              </div>
            <blockquote>
              <div align="left"><a href="http://www.southcarolinastatemuseum.org/exhibits/civilwar.aspx" target="_blank">The
